Package: OrchidGermClass
Title: Orchid germination prediction
Version: 1.0.0.000
Authors@R: 
    person("Spyridon", "Oikonomidis", , "soikonomidis@biol.uoa.gr", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: The present package aims to use seed morphological, habitat, phylogenetic data for orchid taxa to classify their germination with the goal to be used as an initial screening tool of germination behaviour for orchid species.
